"在jump list中跳转
"输入普通数字表示向后跳转(<C-O>),数字之前加个'+'表示向前跳转(<C-I>)
nnoremap <leader>j :call GotoJump()<CR>
function! GotoJump()
  jumps
  let j = input("Please select your jump: ")
  if j != ''
    let pattern = '\v\c^\+'
    if j =~ pattern
      let j = substitute(j, pattern, '', 'g')
      execute "normal " . j . "\<c-i>"
    else
      execute "normal " . j . "\<c-o>"
    endif
  endif
endfunction

